news.headline: This Strength Of The Labor Market And Economy, Amid Accelerating Inflation, Puts The Fed Back Into Wait-And-See Mode
news.summary: Nonfarm payrolls jumped by 256,000 in December, after having risen by 212,000 in November, to 159.5 million jobs, according to the Bureau of Labor Statistics today.
